articles.description: Jermaine Marrow totaled 27 points, six rebounds and six assists to lead Hampton to an 82-52 wire-to-wire victory over Norfolk State on Saturday.
articles.headline: Marrow leads Hampton to 82-52 romp over Norfolk State

articles.description: 11 players score for the No. 22 Shockers in a 95-74 home victory against the Huskies.
articles.headline: Wichita State too much for UConn

images.caption: 11 players score for the No. 22 Shockers in a 95-74 home victory against the Huskies.
images.name: Wichita State too much for UConn

articles.description: Steven Haney scored a career-best 31 points and Loyola Marymount held on for an 85-79 win over Pepperdine on Saturday afternoon, snapping a three-game skid.
articles.headline: Loyola Marymount holds on for 85-79 win over Pepperdine

articles.description: Nick King matched his career-high with 32 points, tying the school record with his fourth 30-point game this season, and Middle Tennessee held off North Texas 79-73 to win its seventh straight on Saturday.
articles.headline: King scores 32, MTSU holds off North Texas 79-73

articles.description: Kevin Brown and John Thompson III break down Wichita State's win over UConn and the tough schedule ahead for the Shockers.
articles.headline: Thompson: This is the Wichita State team we've been looking for
